s boy wants you to save a lot<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>You can save from the main menu at any time, but this may take a while to just grind out.<\/p>\n<p>A far better way of completing this task is to <em>enable Save Prompts<\/em> in the Game Settings screen, accessed from the same menu.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/018\/03-pokemon-unbound-saving-with-prompts.jpg\" alt=\"Saving with prompts \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Saving with prompts<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>During the course of the main storyline, you\u2019ll be prompted to save at important moments, and these add up. <\/p>\n<p>In a normal playthrough, by the time you beat the Pok\u00e9mon League you will probably have been prompted to save at least a hundred times.<\/p>\n<p>The reward for saving 100 times is a Bottle Cap.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/018\/04-pokemon-unbound-your-reward-for-saving-often.jpg\" alt=\"Your reward for saving often \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Your reward for saving often<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong cla